46 required by the court, the court shall issue a warrant for the arrest of the monitored
47 individual. The monitored individual remains responsible for the full contracted fee
48 that is lawfully owed to the provider through the date the provider’s device is
49 actually removed.
50 (b) Upon removal of the device, the provider shall promptly notify the court,
51 the district attorney, the monitored individual, and any affected surety that the device
